text: Rolf Bietmann (born 18 May 1954) is a German politician. He represents the CDU. Bietmann has served as a member of the Bundestag from the state of North Rhine-Westphalia from 2002 till 2005. ==External links== * Web Archive of the German Bundestag of 15 November 2005 Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Bundestag for North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Members of the Bundestag 2002–2005 Category:Christian Democratic Union of Germany politicians Category:Members of the Bundestag for the Christian Democratic Union of Germany
